        {
          "name": "Add Transaction Manually",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "// Test script to validate response",
                  "pm.test('Status code is 200', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Response has success field', function () {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('success');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (jsonData.success) {",
                  "        console.log('✅ Transaction added successfully');",
                  "        console.log('Transaction ID:', jsonData.data.transaction_log_id);",
                  "        console.log('User ID:', jsonData.data.user_id);",
                  "        console.log('Amount:', jsonData.data.amount);",
                  "        console.log('Expiry Date:', jsonData.data.expiry_date);",
                  "    }",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"vrajsurani606@gmail.com\",\n  \"contact\": \"9876543210\",\n  \"method\": \"Razorpay\",\n  \"transaction_id\": \"TXN_{{$timestamp}}\",\n  \"currency_code\": \"INR\",\n  \"price_amount\": 999,\n  \"paid_amount\": 999,\n  \"plan_id\": 1,\n  \"usage_purpose\": \"professional\",\n  \"fromWallet\": 0,\n  \"fromWhere\": \"Mobile\",\n  \"coins\": 0\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{api_base_url}}/order-user/add-transaction-manually",
              "host": [
                "{{api_base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "order-user",
                "add-transaction-manually"
              ]
            },
            "description": "⚠️ AUTHENTICATION REQUIRED\n\n**Manually add subscription transaction for a user**\n\n### Required Fields:\n- `email` (string, email): User email address (must exist in database)\n- `contact` (string, max 15): User contact number\n- `method` (string): Payment method (e.g., Razorpay, PhonePe, Bank Transfer)\n- `transaction_id` (string): Unique transaction ID (auto-generated with timestamp in example)\n- `currency_code` (string): INR or USD\n- `price_amount` (number): Original plan price\n- `paid_amount` (number): Amount actually paid\n- `plan_id` (integer): Subscription plan ID\n- `usage_purpose` (string): personal or professional\n\n### Optional Fields:\n- `fromWallet` (boolean): 0 or 1 (default: 0)\n- `fromWhere` (string): Source (Mobile/Web/Manual)\n- `coins` (integer): Coins to add (default: 0)\n\n### What This API Does:\n1. ✅ Validates user exists and is active\n2. ✅ Validates plan exists\n3. ✅ Checks transaction ID is unique\n4. ✅ Creates transaction log entry\n5. ✅ Deactivates old subscriptions\n6. ✅ Sets new expiry date based on plan validity\n7. ✅ Updates user premium status\n8. ✅ Updates personal details with usage purpose\n\n### Response Structure:\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Transaction added successfully\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"transaction_log_id\": 123,\n    \"user_id\": 456,\n    \"transaction_id\": \"TXN123456789\",\n    \"amount\": 999,\n    \"currency\": \"INR\",\n    \"plan_name\": \"Professional Plan\",\n    \"expiry_date\": \"2026-03-23 15:30:00\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### Error Responses:\n- **404**: User not found or Plan not found\n- **400**: User account inactive or Transaction ID already exists\n- **422**: Validation failed\n- **500**: Server error\n\n### Notes:\n- Transaction ID is auto-generated with timestamp to avoid duplicates\n- Old subscriptions are automatically deactivated\n- User becomes premium immediately\n- Expiry date is calculated from current date + plan validity days"
          }
        }
